{"tid":573734,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[負能樣] 一人n個見過最乞人憎嘅人#yup#","createTime":"2018-02-26T17:30:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-26T17:38:38.000Z","uid":68691,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"27c6d67170260f1adcbf143bd06cecdda7eaed92","tid":573734,"uid":68691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T17:30:55.000Z","msg":"因為生啱年代而家衣食無憂嘅老屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 郁啲就屌後生仔廢青唔捱得乜乜乜<br />\n<br />\n得閒無事就搞風搞雨嘅小學雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 專係做啲乞人憎嘢嚟激嬲人<br />\n<br />\n知少少扮代表嘅自大精<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知憑乜周圍笑鳩人<br />\n<br />\n天堂有路佢不走嘅煩膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咁同人散播負能量但又唔肯主動脫離苦海<br />\n<br />\n係咁俾伏人踩嘅偽善怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跣親人重想扮冇事發生<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d1534b98eff2b9973caab2db6458c43912baaff","tid":573734,"uid":21423,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T17:31:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"25682126c9af05d82029efd61a5de3f6b278fe75","tid":573734,"uid":136760,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2d1534b98eff2b9973caab2db6458c43912baaff","tid":573734,"uid":21423,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T17:31:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T17:36:16.000Z","msg":"得閒無事就搞風搞雨嘅小學雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 專係做啲乞人憎嘢嚟激嬲人"},{"pid":"5f803eb0d6d78ab5a523d475da676452ed4cac1c","tid":573734,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d1534b98eff2b9973caab2db6458c43912baaff","tid":573734,"uid":21423,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T17:31:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被